{"tid":1598792,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"有關 LIHKG Android 無法正常閱讀主題的更新資訊","createTime":"2019-09-27T16:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T17:41:32.000Z","uid":179338,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0f55d957e8ec0d64678e2465d3120efc5558ba50","tid":1598792,"uid":179338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 近日收到頗多 LIHKG Android 16.2.2 版本有關無法正常閱讀主題嘅回報，大多數係「黑Mon」嘅問題，經測試後發現問題成因可能因為過於頻繁嘅轉頁動作引致。<br />\n新版本會就呢個問題作出修正，不便之處謹此致歉。<br />\n<br />\n鑑於今次問題而發現橫向閱讀模式轉頁對於單手操作非常唔方便，<br />\n是次更新將會喺橫向閱讀模式右下角嘅「跳至最底」捷徑加入新動作<br />\n新功能：橫向閱讀模式長按「跳至最底」捷徑會顯示頁數選單<br />\n（垂直閱讀模式轉頁只需要向左拉出選單即可，故並無加入此捷徑）<br />\n另外，長按橫向閱讀模式頂部的頁數條亦可轉頁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c4e4Qvr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc4e4Qvr.gif&h=1848fa99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新版本 16.2.3 將會先於Beta 版本推出，於測試後將會提供正式版本更新；<br />\n若閣下希望參與 LIHKG Android Beta 測試計劃<br />\n可以按此：<a href=\"https://play.google.com/apps/testing/com.lihkg.app\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fapps%2Ftesting%2Fcom.lihkg.app&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHb9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=c63f3dfd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/apps/testing/com.lihkg.app</a><br />\n點擊「成為測試人員」，稍後將會於 Google Play 獲得 Beta 版本更新<br />\n注意：Beta 測試版可能會有未預期的錯誤、較不穩定，遇到問題時請踴躍回報，問題回報有助我們改進應用程式體驗。<br />\n<br />\n再次感謝各位回報問題，亦感激各位參與 Beta 測試<br />\n<br />\n為方便用戶回報問題，LIHKG Android 開發團隊最近試驗性啟用 Telegram 帳號<br />\n請喺回報問題時詳細描述發生問題的經過，閣下應用程式版本、Android 版本等資訊<br />\n呢啲資訊將會有助我哋更快搵到問題成因。<br />\n<br />\n請留意，LIHKG Android 開發團隊只會跟進有關 Android 應用程式問題<br />\n而<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不會</span></span></strong>向你詢問 / 處理任何有關閣下帳號的資訊<br />\n若閣下有帳號或其他站務疑問，歡迎電郵到 info@lihkg.com<br />\n閣下亦請切勿提供 / 透露任何個人資訊，LIHKG Android 開發團隊<span style=\"color: red;\">不會</span>透過任何方式索取，或以任何方式向你認證用戶身份。<br />\nLIHKG Android 開發團隊 Telegram 帳號：<a href=\"https://t.me/LIHKGAndroid\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FLIHKGAndroid&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHb9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=6ce74161\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/LIHKGAndroid</a><br />\n<strong><em> <br />\n** 請緊記以 Secret Chat 模式通訊 **<br />\n** LIHKG Android 只有此 Telegram 帳號，並<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有</span></span>於其他社交媒體/通訊軟件註冊；如有疑問，歡迎以電郵聯絡 info@lihkg.com **<br />\n</em></strong>"},{"pid":"4773172f2181a38de1cef3f7efe29343a61dbfad","tid":1598792,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:02:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6bd55db693bc5a992b60ecfdc852ba197458a728","tid":1598792,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:02:59.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"c56b61f8a96630c3c7704879053a0373fe38150e","tid":1598792,"uid":305631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:05:29.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"b1f20c445cd7e1a7c3814acbd60e6492eda530e8","tid":1598792,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:08:13.000Z","msg":"德政<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff715303652155c9f2c7b3d5778a2aee1be9ef22","tid":1598792,"uid":43806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:09:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54486e2d23a56617842d2d70158b837527cdd885","tid":1598792,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:11:00.000Z","msg":"928 929 1001<br />\n到時見<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f681063faf9788b4e2a1c32d707ebbe0abf47614","tid":1598792,"uid":179338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:37:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"